---
title: Creamy Roasted Turkey Divan with Broccoli and Smashed Potatoes
description: A family classic gets a tasty, modern makeover! This deconstructed riff on the popular casserole is rounded out by a side of smashed potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-roasted-turkey-divan-eb27e8ba.jpg
